Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收手吧 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意欲何為 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道兄長你的性慾乃大陸首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然放著眼前的妹妹不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將魔手伸向嘉依卡 實在是不能坐視不理呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽點太多我都不知從哪吐起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我聲明我是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您太謙虛了 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無防備睡在一旁的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對兄長你來說 不就如同擺在猛獸眼前的生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我當成什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奇伊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得啊 值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何貴幹? 又帶來了什麼新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了下一位英雄的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞 科尼柯賽克王國的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後確認其行蹤是在四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離這三日車程的 拉德米歐市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少能當作個追尋他的線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實打從一開始就全都知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 至少我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不過是一名使者罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得是上了你的套 令人很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 那挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情地懷疑 苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正希望你們如此

Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不歸谷

Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走過路過不要錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有南方礦山挖出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高純度的魔法思念料喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 品種齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要 這個也買
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不歸谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是個經常佈滿濃霧的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可自從四年前起 一點也不放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入谷者沒人再出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出了棄獸啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟就連去確認的人們 也都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知都還是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失蹤? 西蒙·斯坎尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這男人原來是軍中的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但戰爭結束後 馬上就失去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 沒想到被稱作英雄的男人竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些日子的阿巴爾特伯爵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認已經病死的多明妮卡·斯考達也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為輝煌的八英雄的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不免感到詫異啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還有傳聞 說這是賈茲皇帝的詛咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詛咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼活了五百年 能使用怪物般的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟那是個有著各種詭異傳說的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳聞先不說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但賈茲皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是從金錢的角度 或是作為高純度的魔法思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是無以倫比的絕品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此說不定得到它 會導致人們喪失正常的判斷力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若嘉依卡一行人打算接觸西蒙·斯坎尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就應該會在這拉德米歐市現身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會繼續調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正馭使小梟進行探查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想確認下 他有沒有在聚精會神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也別用針刺他頭來試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「針」對你來說 就如同對我來說的「劍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不應該輕易拔出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器能救人 也能傷人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重選擇使用之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到那隊嘉依卡·賈茲及亂破師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在城市另一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞 住所不歸谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正好和他消失的時期相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這個可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 準備機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持隨時能發動的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 離這麼遠也能感知到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面應該還有魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做無益的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白日做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·賈茲 我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收集賈茲皇帝的遺體 到底有什麼企圖?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭悼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說 你的目的就僅僅如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能輕信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肯定是她為了逃走而隨口編的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 嘉依卡能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去做掉基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼勝算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰意已決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就全力以赴 一決雌雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士 亞伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此對汝等宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是廝殺?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯真不公平!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我一份啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她們同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我情願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想跑呢 幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~? 那廝殺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想我死在其他人之手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 再晚一點就危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 全部遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再買不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢? 回機車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那幫傢伙還在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不方便接近城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往北邊飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越過森林應該有個濃霧山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯現吧 探測者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探測魔法 無效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…那也是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法? 那霧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理論上 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 龐大力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力源 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性 有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之不能貿然下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想從空中觀察一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能載著我們 去山谷上方轉一圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為托魯你言而無信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是 明明說好幫你就和我打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒說不和你打啊 總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天是幾時?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天? 明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天就是總有一天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 不管管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體 這下面 探索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我還能怎麼辦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做了那個時候的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到現在我仍偶爾會想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時從懸崖上摔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許活下來的不該是我 而是阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 不要責備自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆因一直有托魯在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我世上最重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說也是 若我沒遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也過不上這樣充實的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因有你在我身邊 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然應儘早處理掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 請求 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情 不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可能性 魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影 精神支配 多重效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯的妄想 成形顯現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等我啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神影響 霧所變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘉依卡 以及建築 全都是霧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…既然會見到那種幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說兄長心中有那樣的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下流無恥 必須立即喚醒兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除結界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守護者」魔法效果範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除 立即 與霧接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到精神支配 與托魯同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是不能吸到霧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能在這眼睜睜看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法 只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 到這邊來 良機到來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法解除 托魯捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法再度 起動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這旅途也接近尾聲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只剩下一件遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打敗亞伯力克·基烈特搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不用再收集遺體了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接你了 嘉依卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞伯力克!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞伯力克?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要與亞伯力克結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈? 結婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 那收集遺體呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要和亞伯力克在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的遺體自然就能到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我好高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我祭悼完父親 我們就舉辦婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可你不是說要和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為一國的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然是要挑選個門當戶對的對象才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可能一直和個低賤亂破師混在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 至今多謝你啦托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會無期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 請等等 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拋棄我嗎~~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要丟下我獨自一人~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦啦 醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來一切都是幻覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔下來時 只有托魯沒能回收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到結界外 就又幻覺叢生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本無法移動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干涉魔法 霧中擊入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方魔法 部分妨害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊入魔法的那一部分 就可以自由行走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法發動 移動 反復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 然後再破壞掉對方的機杖就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 那個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是出於什麼目的才施加了這種魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到本人直接問他就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若他還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統率者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統率者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eim Halmus Rom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naint milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來魔法解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒禮貌 擅自闖入別人家中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西蒙·斯坎尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞掉了 真是不中用的廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底魔法這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵時刻就連個屁用都頂不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是西蒙·斯坎尼亞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙? 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什麼西蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得八英雄中有這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然變化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再回軍隊 絕不回…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部隊位置被敵人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點就死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我之外 大家全死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬魯克那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙把部隊出賣給了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那混蛋 還擺出一副好友的嘴臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬魯克的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 馬魯克那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是在講戰爭時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還把艾蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的至愛妻子奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個那個都是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都給我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到了同伴和妻子的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是離開軍隊 獨自住在了這樣的山谷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 剛才的魔法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪被騙的人自己傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣 絕望 然後全都化為白骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是想讓人看到被信任之人背叛的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人也遭受和他同樣的經歷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體 返還 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 女兒 賈茲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賈茲 女兒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親祭悼 遺體 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那正可謂這世上最無用的破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要就趕緊拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們拿走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼? 捨不得?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 那種東西我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 若要回拉德米歐市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能爬上這崖壁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明被稱作英雄 還得到了財產和遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下場卻這麼悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想那麼多也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這倒不是因為善良…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻覺 我與托魯兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘛 別太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 背叛 不會 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講起來 那怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎會和嘉依卡那樣…對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過畢竟阿卡莉和芙蕾多妮卡是絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也許只好選了嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 為什麼我是絕對不可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 想想就知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…你好像生氣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛中!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山嶺的帝國?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樸實的人們 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 大家 故鄉一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我 祖國記憶 基本沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第八集 「暫慰的帝國」

